# Atlas MVP Data Requirements

## Objective

Identify the minimum data required to support Atlas core workflows.

---

# Workflow 1: Find Representation

Required Data

- Lobbyist Name
- Lobbying Firm
- State
- Registration Status
- Active Clients
- Issue Areas
- Contact Information (if public)
- Registration Dates

---

# Workflow 2: Evaluate Representation

Required Data

- Lobbyist
- Firm
- Active Clients
- Historical Clients
- Industry Categories
- State Coverage
- Estimated Cost
- Potential Conflicts

---

# Workflow 3: Monitor Competitors

Required Data

- Client Name
- Lobbying Firm
- Lobbyist
- Registration Date
- Registration Status
- New Registrations
- Expired Registrations
- State

---

# Workflow 4: Monitor Issues

Required Data

- Issue Area
- Lobbyists
- Firms
- Clients
- State
- Registration Activity

---

# Workflow 5: Market Intelligence

Required Data

- Industry
- State
- Client
- Firm
- Estimated Spend
- Registration Trends

---

# Workflow 6: Vendor Discovery

Required Data

- Lobbyist
- Firm
- Client Base
- Industry Experience
- Geographic Coverage
- Estimated Cost
- Conflict Analysis

